00:02:32.082 --> 00:02:36.726
For days, I sat and looked at his hands,

00:02:36.750 --> 00:02:39.532
the ones that yielded the knife,

00:02:41.883 --> 00:02:45.724
and against his pasty white skin,

00:02:46.589 --> 00:02:48.028
his eyes ...

00:02:48.820 --> 00:02:52.176
Well, he spent endless days in his cell,

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:53.782
no sunlight,

00:02:53.806 --> 00:02:57.693
so his eyes were as black
as his hair and his mustache.

00:02:58.609 --> 00:03:01.393
He was very intimidating,